<a class='reflink' href='../4.paois/4.2.tappgog.html#lemmatopologygroupoidgerms'>4.2.10</a>

<!-- 4.2.10 -->
<div class='toload lemma'>
	<p><span class='envidentifier'>Lemma 4.2.10</span>
	For every $s\in S$ and $U\subseteq X_{s^*}$, let
	<div class='equation'>\[
		[s,U]=\left\lbrace[s, x]\in S\ltimes X : x\in U\right\rbrace.
	\]</div>
	The collection $\mathcal{B}_{\mathrm{germ}}$ of all sets of the form $[s,U]$, where $s\in S$ and $U$ is an open subset of $X_{s^*}$, is a basis for a topology on $S\ltimes X$.
	</p>
</div>